-- Seattle Mariners Sign Pitcher Kevin Millwood to a Minor-League Contract
-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 2012-01-24T18:51:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/seattle-mariners-sign-pitcher-kevin-millwood-to-a-minor-league-contract.html
The  Seattle Mariners  signed starting
pitcher Kevin Millwood to a minor-league contract and invited
him to spring training, the Major League Baseball team said.  Millwood, 37, has a record of 163-140 with a 4.10 earned-
run average during a 15-year career spent with Atlanta,
Philadelphia,  Cleveland ,  Texas , Baltimore and  Colorado .  The righthander threw a no-hitter for Philadelphia in 2003.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  